2ï¸âƒ£ Why do we use Matrix?

We use matrix when data naturally fits in rows & columns.

Real-life reasons:
Situation	Why Matrix
Student marks	Student Ã— Subject
Images	Pixels Ã— Pixels
Games	Board / Grid
