3ï¸âƒ£ Matrix vs Array (VERY IMPORTANT)
Array (1D)	Matrix (2D)
One direction	Two directions
arr[i]	mat[i][j]
Simple list	Table / grid
Linear problems	Grid problems

ğŸ‘‰ If problem mentions:

rows

columns

grid

table

board

â¡ï¸ Use matrix

